reviewText: More Run of The mill Women's Wrestling! Some of it Was good, Some others Not So Much! But Hey they Don't have The WWE's Budget!

i wanted sexy women fighting in a ring...what i got were over weight wrestlers in well covered tights, not even showing cleveage, and only once did i see tight denim shorts on a hot body............the wrestling wasn't too bad, but in no way are these girls athletes, very disappointed
